{"tid":1635104,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"不知境外研究 科學家聯署求習解網禁","createTime":"2019-10-07T11:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T12:16:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cd5f6424802031e17eed4d1014b70ddb7c9794b2","tid":1635104,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:57:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20191006/QRDUJ5J642Q4JUXCMLM5LBPMZI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20191006%2FQRDUJ5J642Q4JUXCMLM5LBPMZI%2F&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nPsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=14069d0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20191006%2FQRDUJ5J642Q4JUXCMLM5LBPMZI%2F&h=1e6785a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20191006/QRDUJ5J642Q4JUXCMLM5LBPMZI/</a><br />\n<br />\n不知境外研究 科學家聯署求習解網禁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/CgXZP60SCZd6m2B0KTC42wk78oE=/190x124/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/V2EWY6BNF7WJSPCEUIZI65OB6E.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FCgXZP60SCZd6m2B0KTC42wk78oE%3D%2F190x124%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FV2EWY6BNF7WJSPCEUIZI65OB6E.gif&h=74e23640&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國收緊網絡審查，有網警協助監察網絡。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】內地網民對北京理工大學三名師生的反應如此大，皆因中共網絡「防火長城」阻隔下，民眾主要靠VPN「翻牆」獲取境外資訊，一旦有關專利技術獲推廣，勢令翻牆的網民被網警「追蹤」風險大增。網民轟他們為虎作倀，連《環球時報》總編胡錫進也抱怨翻牆難，稱中國人民的「網絡幸福感有待提升」。<br />\n<br />\n中共從2017年起，嚴格限制使用VPN；網信辦先命令三大國營電訊公司中移動、中聯通和中電信禁止個人用戶連接VPN；又下令所有提供VPN服務的內地公司下架應用軟件，並以「非法經營」名義處罰27家經營VPN公司；又封殺境外提供VPN服務的公司；甚至對多位「非法出售」VPN的內地民眾刑拘判罰。<br />\n<br />\n中共做法引起內地科研人員不滿；2016年初，78位中國科學院、中國工程院院士聯名上書，向習近平訴苦，指網絡封鎖令他們無法了解境外科研進展，影響研究，要求解禁讓科學家們「共享國際科研成果」。當局最後不得不給這些科學家開後門，讓他們「翻牆」瀏覽國外資訊。"},{"pid":"5c0170dbd170b10d956d2154f249b61fef6bc83f","tid":1635104,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:58:22.000Z","msg":"【行動】緊急！要突破分化！我有三個錦囊俾大家！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634772</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上為節錄內容，覺得有道理請睇全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634772</a>"},{"pid":"0dfbc313ba7f81dad53b7142b103183c3a7f9ba3","tid":1635104,"uid":112622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:59:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"772a023553917fd6ea1e9de5b2147244fdd29277","tid":1635104,"uid":62714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:01:08.000Z","msg":"無得翻牆點抄啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a83f4118d7b023623f56bff83ce20e854635f35","tid":1635104,"uid":178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:16:01.000Z","msg":"咪撚放啲癲狗出嚟"}]}